How To Build the showMeeverything QML/C++ GUI

--- On Unix:

cd ~/showMeEverything/showmeeverything_gui
qmake showmeeverything_gui.pro
make
sudo make install   # or su -c 'make install'

This project requires Qt5.

Optional: If you want the CLI in a different location, adjust the `target.path` in the .pro file or create symlinks.

